{"tid":58450,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[生涯規劃]big4 one year intern求意見諗到頭爆","createTime":"2016-12-28T22:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T15:58:39.000Z","uid":70092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9659d9f32f535be17fd5d5898bb859ac003d9b53","tid":58450,"uid":70092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T22:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鳩痕報左個big4 one year intern,  advisory果邊有 offer<br />\n<br />\n我自己情况係三太 gpa低到好撚低，不過都多細 firm工作經驗，未有明確 career path<br />\n<br />\n應唔應該去做？因為我自己 gpa已經低到一定要 defer一年，所以計埋 intern兩年無撚曬青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗極都唔知點行好"},{"pid":"e0c1a8c7cc9d2ed5fce72680be7aac93a385d6c0","tid":58450,"uid":70092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T23:04:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c482f3b12253d6162e44a73f4ad00fed780ad47","tid":58450,"uid":11019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T23:39:18.000Z","msg":"入big4 短廿年命"},{"pid":"0b1a38ebc3451a2de6de9c017cf4ad9aeeb5b591","tid":58450,"uid":48032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"揾第一份工，GPA相對黎講比較重要，除非你有關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  3大都係噤話<br />\nBig 4intern 會易d出return offer 如果唔係做得太柒<br />\n起碼到你grad，有份唔錯既工先，再騎牛搵馬<br />\n再講青春，你噤低gpa，可能只係搵到份8,9千蚊既工，仲要浮浮沉沉唔知幾多年，到時就唔係浪費兩年青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aababb60ecd49190f8b5f0d7396d159c514e1d8f","tid":58450,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"敢問樓主咩gpa mid 2.x? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f700c6bdc7535619c44375da3588f23066c7ef9","tid":58450,"uid":2240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:24:01.000Z","msg":"係我一定做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做完你會好感恩呢個intern救左你一命<br />\n我都係三大gpa爛到仆街<br />\n好彩有間唔錯既firm收左做1年intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後靠呢份野grad前攞左唔少offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你advisory既位就算grad job都好多人爭<br />\n攞住1年exp 搵consulting firm做都容易好多<br />\nbig4既advisory甚至幫到你搵d corp fin既entry job<br />\n前途會唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家用兩年（計埋defer）<br />\n會幫到你改變命運"},{"pid":"de5beb97f48be5b458a506667cf9f68fa1d9ca75","tid":58450,"uid":47113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"advisory唔錯<br />\n it 向定deals 向<br />\n<br />\n比心機做一年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130129867b6076c9b0c5872eb0c8c4827f762b29","tid":58450,"uid":40247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:06:52.000Z","msg":"低gpa都申請到？"},{"pid":"e91bbbc9f237ee0c1d849f9ba66932b6ea9b3b66","tid":58450,"uid":70092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然搵番個 post多謝大家意見<br />\n果陣都諗住做不過因為一 d on9 原因去唔成<br />\n近排再報第二間再得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n回番上邊我所謂爛既 gpa係爛到得1點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都覺得自己係垃圾黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望做一年big4洗洗底"},{"pid":"16bce1f984657767a7182f3df79e52c9a33c34e5","tid":58450,"uid":103379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />突然搵番個 post多謝大家意見<br />\n果陣都諗住做不過因為一 d on9 原因去唔成<br />\n近排再報第二間再得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n回番上邊我所謂